Before using microservice people uses monolithic approach.
Monolithic approach people used to create every services individually and at final combined as a single .war file and being deployed it to the server.

Disadvantages of Monolithic:
  Performance issues
  Continuous deployment is not possible
  Adopting new technologies will be difficult
  Overloaded IDE & Overloaded Web container
  Exception propagation not proper
  Code readable is not there.
